emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group of young men, and women, including one wearing eyeglasses, light colored short sleeved round scoop neckline dress, and small button earrings, seated at tables in Centre Avenue YMCA for Youth Conference
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1956, pg. A29 reads: "Listen Attentively - Delegates to the Youth Conference held at the Centre Avenue YMCA last week-end listen attentively as the Rev. Virgil D. Moccia, of Bidwell Presbyterian Church, speaks to them. Over 100 young people attended. - Harris Photo."
